[2026-05-19T01:34:11.379Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_kw62nogn8jk8_2","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Library Screen Specification\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Screen Title\n4\t\n5\t**Library**\n6\t\n7\t---\n8\t\n9\t## 2. Purpose\n10\t\n11\tPersonal bookshelf tab serving as a navigation hub to Health Log, Mood & Wellness, and Education entry points. Part of the 4-tab bottom navigation shell. This screen provides quick access to health tracking and wellness resources, acting as a central discovery point for personal health management tools.\n12\t\n13\t---\n14\t\n15\t## 3. Route\n16\t\n17\t`/library`\n18\t\n19\t---\n20\t\n21\t## 4. Widget Name\n22\t\n23\t`LibraryScreen`\n24\t\n25\t---\n26\t\n27\t## 5. Design Tokens\n28\t\n29\t### Color Palette (from DESIGN.md)\n30\t\n31\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n32\t|---|---|---|\n33\t| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, active nav indicator, Health Log icon |\n34\t| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, Mood & Wellness icon |\n35\t| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Tertiary, success states, Education icon |\n36\t| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n37\t| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n38\t| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text (titles, descriptions) |\n39\t| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, descriptions |\n40\t| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Card borders if needed |\n41\t| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background |\n42\t\n43\t### Typography (Google Fonts — Nunito)\n44\t\n45\t| Style | Size | Weight | Usage |\n46\t|---|---|---|---|\n47\t| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | AppBar title |\n48\t| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | Card titles |\n49\t| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | Body text |\n50\t| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | Secondary text, descriptions |\n51\t| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | Button text |\n52\t| `caption` | 12sp | 500 | Badges, timestamps |\n53\t\n54\t### Spacing Rhythm (base 8dp)\n55\t\n56\t| Token | Value |\n57\t|---|---|\n58\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n59\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n60\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n61\t| `md` | 16dp |\n62\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n63\t| `xl` | 32dp |\n64\t| `xxl` | 48dp |\n65\t\n66\t### Corner Radius\n67\t\n68\t| Token | Value |\n69\t|---|---|\n70\t| `sm` | 8dp |\n71\t| `md` | 12dp |\n72\t| `lg` | 16dp |\n73\t| `pill` | 999dp |\n74\t\n75\t### Motion\n76\t\n77\t| Token | Value |\n78\t|---|---|---|\n79\t| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n80\t| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n81\t| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n82\t| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n83\t\n84\t---\n85\t\n86\t## 6. Layout Rules\n87\t\n88\t### Scaffold Structure\n89\t\n90\t- `Scaffold` with `SingleChildScrollView` as body (no slivers needed — simple card list)\n91\t- `AppBar`: title \"Library\", no leading (tab screen), no FAB\n92\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: visible (4 tabs, index 2 = Library active)\n93\t- Safe area: 12dp top padding for status bar, 80dp bottom for nav + home indicator\n94\t\n95\t### AppBar Behavior\n96\t\n97\t- Transparent background blending to `lavenderTint`\n98\t- Title: \"Library\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite`)\n99\t- No back button (tab screen)\n100\t- No actions\n101\t\n102\t### Body Layout\n103\t\n104\t- `SingleChildScrollView` as body\n105\t- `Padding` with 16dp horizontal\n106\t- `Column` with `mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min` containing card sections\n107\t- 24dp vertical spacing between card sections\n108\t- Bottom padding: 24dp to clear bottom nav\n109\t\n110\t---\n111\t\n112\t## 7. Sections\n113\t\n114\t### Section 1: Health Log Link Card\n115\t\n116\t**Description:** Navigation card leading to the unified health timeline.\n117\t\n118\t**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n119\t\n120\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n121\t\n122\t**Components:**\n123\t- 48dp circular icon container with `lavenderBloom` at 15% opacity fill\n124\t- Icon: `Icons.favorite_outline` (24sp, `lavenderBloom`)\n125\t- Title: \"Health Log\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n126\t- Description: \"Track symptoms, doctor visits, reminders\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n127\t- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n128\t\n129\t**Interactive:** Tap → `context.push('/health-log')`\n130\t\n131\t**Scale feedback:** 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n132\t\n133\t---\n134\t\n135\t### Section 2: Mood & Wellness Link Card\n136\t\n137\t**Description:** Navigation card leading to mood and energy tracking.\n138\t\n139\t**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n140\t\n141\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n142\t\n143\t**Components:**\n144\t- 48dp circular icon container with `blushRose` at 20% opacity fill\n145\t- Icon: `Icons.mood_outlined` (24sp, `blushRose`)\n146\t- Title: \"Mood & Wellness\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n147\t- Description: \"Log moods, track energy levels\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n148\t- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n149\t\n150\t**Interactive:** Tap → `context.push('/mood-wellness')`\n151\t\n152\t**Scale feedback:** 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n153\t\n154\t---\n155\t\n156\t### Section 3: Education Link Card\n157\t\n158\t**Description:** Navigation card leading to educational content browser.\n159\t\n160\t**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n161\t\n162\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n163\t\n164\t**Components:**\n165\t- 48dp circular icon container with `softMint` at 20% opacity fill\n166\t- Icon: `Icons.school_outlined` (24sp, `softMint`)\n167\t- Title: \"Education\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n168\t- Description: \"Browse articles and trusted health info\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n169\t- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n170\t\n171\t**Interactive:** Tap → `context.push('/education')`\n172\t\n173\t**Scale feedback:** 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n174\t\n175\t---\n176\t\n177\t## 8. Data\n178\t\n179\t**Entities Consumed:**\n180\t| Entity | Provider | Fields Used |\n181\t|---|---|---|\n182\t| None | — | Library is purely navigational |\n183\t\n184\tThis screen serves as a discovery hub — all data is shown on destination screens. No state providers are directly consumed by this screen.\n185\t\n186\t---\n187\t\n188\t## 9. Motion\n189\t\n190\t### Entry Animations\n191\t\n192\t- Screen loads with fade-in: 300ms, `easeOut`\n193\t- Cards use staggered entry: 100ms delay between each card, 300ms fade per card\n194\t- Total stagger duration: 500ms for all three cards\n195\t\n196\t### Interactive Feedback\n197\t\n198\t- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms ease-out return\n199\t- Bottom nav indicator: 200ms ease-in-out glide between tab positions\n200\t\n201\t### Anti-Motion\n202\t\n203\t- All animations respect `MediaQuery.disableAnimations`\n204\t- `prefers-reduced-motion` media query honored — when enabled, skip all animations\n205\t\n206\t---\n207\t\n208\t## 10. Accessibility\n209\t\n210\t### Semantic Labels\n211\t\n212\t| Element | Label |\n213\t|---|---|\n214\t| AppBar | `'Library screen'` |\n215\t| Health Log card | `'Health Log, double tap to open health log screen'` |\n216\t| Mood & Wellness card | `'Mood and Wellness, double tap to open mood and wellness screen'` |\n217\t| Education card | `'Education, double tap to open education screen'` |\n218\t\n219\t### Focus Order\n220\t\n221\t1. Health Log card\n222\t2. Mood & Wellness card\n223\t3. Education card\n224\t4. Bottom navigation items (in order: Home, Browse, Library, Profile)\n225\t\n226\t### Contrast Notes\n227\t\n228\t- `lavenderBloom` (#7C3AED) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~5.2:1 (AA compliant)\n229\t- `deepGraphite` (#1F2937) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~12:1 (AAA compliant)\n230\t- `stoneGrey` (#6B7280) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~4.7:1 (AA borderline — used for descriptions only)\n231\t\n232\t### Touch Target Compliance\n233\t\n234\t- All cards: full card area, minimum 48dp height\n235\t- Icon containers: 48dp diameter\n236\t- All interactive elements meet 48dp minimum touch target\n237\t\n238\t---\n239\t\n240\t## 11. Anti-Patterns\n241\t\n242\t**Do Not:**\n243\t- Add a FAB to Library screen (tab screens don't have FABs per UX.md)\n244\t- Use `CustomScrollView` with slivers (not needed for simple card list — use `SingleChildScrollView`)\n245\t- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only)\n246\t- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n247\t- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n248\t- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n249\t- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n250\t- Add more than the 3 defined link cards\n251\t- Use hero animations (simple push navigation with no shared elements)\n252\t- Add elevation shadows beyond level1 for cards (soft shadow only)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a74ff47c-f0fd-427b-86f4-237d93787cf9","uuid":"d59ea30e-f91b-460e-80a3-c8d14c467e35","timestamp":"2026-05-19T01:34:11.378Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/library/SPEC.md","content":"# Library Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n\n**Library**\n\n---\n\n## 2. Purpose\n\nPersonal bookshelf tab serving as a navigation hub to Health Log, Mood & Wellness, and Education entry points. Part of the 4-tab bottom navigation shell. This screen provides quick access to health tracking and wellness resources, acting as a central discovery point for personal health management tools.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Route\n\n`/library`\n\n---\n\n## 4. Widget Name\n\n`LibraryScreen`\n\n---\n\n## 5. Design Tokens\n\n### Color Palette (from DESIGN.md)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, active nav indicator, Health Log icon |\n| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, Mood & Wellness icon |\n| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Tertiary, success states, Education icon |\n| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text (titles, descriptions) |\n| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, descriptions |\n| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Card borders if needed |\n| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background |\n\n### Typography (Google Fonts — Nunito)\n\n| Style | Size | Weight | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | AppBar title |\n| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | Card titles |\n| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | Body text |\n| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | Secondary text, descriptions |\n| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | Button text |\n| `caption` | 12sp | 500 | Badges, timestamps |\n\n### Spacing Rhythm (base 8dp)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp |\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `sm` | 12dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n| `xl` | 32dp |\n| `xxl` | 48dp |\n\n### Corner Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp |\n| `md` | 12dp |\n| `lg` | 16dp |\n| `pill` | 999dp |\n\n### Motion\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|---|\n| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n\n- `Scaffold` with `SingleChildScrollView` as body (no slivers needed — simple card list)\n- `AppBar`: title \"Library\", no leading (tab screen), no FAB\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: visible (4 tabs, index 2 = Library active)\n- Safe area: 12dp top padding for status bar, 80dp bottom for nav + home indicator\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n\n- Transparent background blending to `lavenderTint`\n- Title: \"Library\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite`)\n- No back button (tab screen)\n- No actions\n\n### Body Layout\n\n- `SingleChildScrollView` as body\n- `Padding` with 16dp horizontal\n- `Column` with `mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min` containing card sections\n- 24dp vertical spacing between card sections\n- Bottom padding: 24dp to clear bottom nav\n\n---\n\n## 7. Sections\n\n### Section 1: Health Log Link Card\n\n**Description:** Navigation card leading to the unified health timeline.\n\n**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n\n**Components:**\n- 48dp circular icon container with `lavenderBloom` at 15% opacity fill\n- Icon: `Icons.favorite_outline` (24sp, `lavenderBloom`)\n- Title: \"Health Log\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n- Description: \"Track symptoms, doctor visits, reminders\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n\n**Interactive:** Tap → `context.push('/health-log')`\n\n**Scale feedback:** 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n\n---\n\n### Section 2: Mood & Wellness Link Card\n\n**Description:** Navigation card leading to mood and energy tracking.\n\n**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n\n**Components:**\n- 48dp circular icon container with `blushRose` at 20% opacity fill\n- Icon: `Icons.mood_outlined` (24sp, `blushRose`)\n- Title: \"Mood & Wellness\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n- Description: \"Log moods, track energy levels\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n\n**Interactive:** Tap → `context.push('/mood-wellness')`\n\n**Scale feedback:** 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n\n---\n\n### Section 3: Education Link Card\n\n**Description:** Navigation card leading to educational content browser.\n\n**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n\n**Components:**\n- 48dp circular icon container with `softMint` at 20% opacity fill\n- Icon: `Icons.school_outlined` (24sp, `softMint`)\n- Title: \"Education\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n- Description: \"Browse articles and trusted health info\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n\n**Interactive:** Tap → `context.push('/education')`\n\n**Scale feedback:** 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n\n---\n\n## 8. Data\n\n**Entities Consumed:**\n| Entity | Provider | Fields Used |\n|---|---|---|\n| None | — | Library is purely navigational |\n\nThis screen serves as a discovery hub — all data is shown on destination screens. No state providers are directly consumed by this screen.\n\n---\n\n## 9. Motion\n\n### Entry Animations\n\n- Screen loads with fade-in: 300ms, `easeOut`\n- Cards use staggered entry: 100ms delay between each card, 300ms fade per card\n- Total stagger duration: 500ms for all three cards\n\n### Interactive Feedback\n\n- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms ease-out return\n- Bottom nav indicator: 200ms ease-in-out glide between tab positions\n\n### Anti-Motion\n\n- All animations respect `MediaQuery.disableAnimations`\n- `prefers-reduced-motion` media query honored — when enabled, skip all animations\n\n---\n\n## 10. Accessibility\n\n### Semantic Labels\n\n| Element | Label |\n|---|---|\n| AppBar | `'Library screen'` |\n| Health Log card | `'Health Log, double tap to open health log screen'` |\n| Mood & Wellness card | `'Mood and Wellness, double tap to open mood and wellness screen'` |\n| Education card | `'Education, double tap to open education screen'` |\n\n### Focus Order\n\n1. Health Log card\n2. Mood & Wellness card\n3. Education card\n4. Bottom navigation items (in order: Home, Browse, Library, Profile)\n\n### Contrast Notes\n\n- `lavenderBloom` (#7C3AED) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~5.2:1 (AA compliant)\n- `deepGraphite` (#1F2937) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~12:1 (AAA compliant)\n- `stoneGrey` (#6B7280) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~4.7:1 (AA borderline — used for descriptions only)\n\n### Touch Target Compliance\n\n- All cards: full card area, minimum 48dp height\n- Icon containers: 48dp diameter\n- All interactive elements meet 48dp minimum touch target\n\n---\n\n## 11. Anti-Patterns\n\n**Do Not:**\n- Add a FAB to Library screen (tab screens don't have FABs per UX.md)\n- Use `CustomScrollView` with slivers (not needed for simple card list — use `SingleChildScrollView`)\n- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only)\n- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n- Add more than the 3 defined link cards\n- Use hero animations (simple push navigation with no shared elements)\n- Add elevation shadows beyond level1 for cards (soft shadow only)","numLines":252,"startLine":1,"totalLines":252}}}
