s | Mood rating 1-5 (displayed as \"4/5\" on home stat card) |\n38\t| energyLevel | int | yes | Energy level 1-5 |\n39\t| notes | String? | no | Optional notes about mood |\n40\t\n41\t## Entity: SymptomEntry\n42\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n43\t|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n44\t| id | String | yes | Unique identifier |\n45\t| date | DateTime | yes | Date symptom was logged |\n46\t| type | SymptomType | yes | Category of symptom |\n47\t| severity | int | yes | Severity level 1-3 (color-coded in UI) |\n48\t| notes | String? | no | Optional description |\n49\t\n50\t## Entity: DoctorVisit\n51\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n52\t|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n53\t| id | String | yes | Unique identifier |\n54\t| date | DateTime | yes | Visit date |\n55\t| doctorName | String? | no | Name of doctor |\n56\t| summary | String | yes | Visit summary |\n57\t| notes | String? | no | Additional notes |\n58\t\n59\t## Entity: Reminder\n60\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n61\t|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n62\t| id | String | yes | Unique identifier |\n63\t| date | DateTime | yes | Reminder date |\n64\t| title | String | yes | Reminder title (e.g. \"Next checkup\") |\n65\t| isDone | bool | yes | Whether the reminder is completed |\n66\t\n67\t## Entity: WeekContent\n68\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n69\t|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n70\t| weekNumber | int | yes | Pregnancy week (1-42) |\n71\t| trimesterLabel | String | yes | e.g. \"Second Trimester\" |\n72\t| sizeComparison | String | yes | Fruit/vegetable analogy (e.g. \"mango\") |\n73\t| milestoneTitle | String? | no | Milestone celebration title (e.g. \"Halfway there!\") |\n74\t| milestoneDescription | String? | no | Milestone celebration body text |\n75\t| bodyChanges | List\\<InfoItem\\> | yes | Body changes for this week |\n76\t| babyDevelopment | List\\<InfoItem\\> | yes | Baby development milestones for this week |\n77\t| selfCareItems | List\\<String\\> | yes | Daily self-care checklist items |\n78\t| exerciseGuides | List\\<String\\> | yes | Safe exercises for current trimester |\n79\t| nutritionTips | List\\<String\\> | yes | Stage-appropriate nutrition tips |\n80\t\n81\t## Entity: InfoItem\n82\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n83\t|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n84\t| title | String | yes | Short heading (e.g. \"Hearing develops\") |\n85\t| description | String | yes | Explanatory text |\n86\t\n87\t## Entity: SelfCareCheckState\n88\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n89\t|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n90\t| weekNumber | int | yes | The pregnancy week this state belongs to |\n91\t| date | DateTime | yes | The date of the checklist |\n92\t| completedItems | List\\<String\\> | yes | List of completed checklist item labels |\n93\t\n94\t## Entity: Article\n95\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n96\t|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n97\t| id | String | yes | Unique identifier |\n98\t| title | String | yes | Article title |\n99\t| topic | ArticleTopic | yes | Topic category for filtering |\n100\t| body | String | yes | Rich text article content |\n101\t| illustrationUrl | String? | no | Hero image URL |\n102\t| readTime | String? | no | Estimated read time (e.g. \"5 min\") |\n103\t| isBookmarked | bool | yes | Whether user has bookmarked this article |\n104\t| relatedArticleIds | List\\<String\\> | yes | IDs of related articles shown at bottom |\n105\t\n106\t## Entity: Exercise\n107\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n108\t|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n109\t| id | String | yes | Unique identifier |\n110\t| name | String | yes | Exercise name |\n111\t| category | ExerciseCategory | yes | Type: breathing, stretching, or meditation |\n112\t| duration | Duration | yes | Estimated duration |\n113\t| steps | List\\<String\\> | yes | Step-by-step instructions |\n114\t| benefits | List\\<String\\> | yes | List of wellness benefits |\n115\t| difficulty | String? | no | Difficulty level label |\n116\t| illustrationUrl | String? | no | Exercise illustration |\n117\t\n118\t## Entity: UserPreferences\n119\t| Field | Type | Required | Description |\n120\t|-------|------|----------|-------------|\n121\t| dailyRemindersEnabled | bool | yes | Toggle for daily reminder notifications |\n122\t| checkupAlertsEnabled | bool | yes | Toggle for checkup alert notifications |\n123\t| selfCareNudgesEnabled | bool | yes | Toggle for self-care nudge notifications |\n124\t| reducedMotionEnabled | bool | yes | Toggle for reduced motion/animations |\n125\t| units | WeightUnit | yes | Preferred weight unit (kg/lbs) |\n126\t\n127\t## Enums\n128\t\n129\t### WeightUnit\n130\t- kg\n131\t- lbs\n132\t\n133\t### SymptomType\n134\t- nausea\n135\t- fatigue\n136\t- headache\n137\t- backPain\n138\t- swelling\n139\t- cramping\n140\t- dizziness\n141\t- other\n142\t\n143\t### ExerciseCategory\n144\t- breathing\n145\t- stretching\n146\t- meditation\n147\t\n148\t### ArticleTopic\n149\t- nutrition\n150\t- bodyChanges\n151\t- maternalCare\n152\t- babyDevelopment\n153\t\n154\t### AppMode\n155\t- pregnancy\n156\t- wellness\n157\t\n158\t### MoodLevel\n159\t- 1 (very low)\n160\t- 2 (low)\n161\t- 3 (neutral)\n162\t- 4 (good)\n163\t- 5 (great)\n164\t\n165\t## Relationships\n166\t- PregnancyProfile has many WeightEntries (1:N via implicit ownership)\n167\t- PregnancyProfile has many CycleEntries (1:N via implicit ownership)\n168\t- PregnancyProfile has many MoodEntries (1:N via implicit ownership)\n169\t- PregnancyProfile has many SymptomEntries (1:N via implicit ownership)\n170\t- PregnancyProfile has many DoctorVisits (1:N via implicit ownership)\n171\t- PregnancyProfile has many Reminders (1:N via implicit ownership)\n172\t- PregnancyProfile has one UserPreferences (1:1)\n173\t- WeekContent is standalone reference data keyed by weekNumber\n174\t- Article is standalone reference data (filterable by ArticleTopic)\n175\t- Exercise is standalone reference data (filterable by ExerciseCategory)\n176\t- Article references many Articles via relatedArticleIds (N:N self-referential)\n177\t\n178\t## Screen to Entity Mapping\n179\t| Screen | Entities Consumed |\n180\t|--------|-------------------|\n181\t| Home | PregnancyProfile, WeightEntry (latest), MoodEntry (latest), Reminder (next), WeekContent (current week) |\n182\t| Cycle Tracking | CycleEntry, PregnancyProfile |\n183\t| Weight & Nutrition | WeightEntry, PregnancyProfile, WeekContent (nutrition tips) |\n184\t| Pregnancy Progress | PregnancyProfile, WeekContent, SelfCareCheckState |\n185\t| Mindfulness | Exercise, MoodEntry (today) |\n186\t| Exercise Detail | Exercise |\n187\t| Health Log | DoctorVisit, SymptomEntry, Reminder |\n188\t| Mood & Wellness | MoodEntry, PregnancyProfile |\n189\t| Education | Article |\n190\t| Article Reader | Article |\n191\t| Settings | PregnancyProfile, UserPreferences |\n192\t\n193\t## Mock Data Requirements\n194\t- 1 PregnancyProfile (week 22, due date ~18 weeks out, name \"Mira\")\n195\t- 15-20 WeightEntries spanning weeks 15-22 (values ~56-59 kg, gradual increase)\n196\t- 3-5 CycleEntries (pre-pregnancy history)\n197\t- 10-14 MoodEntries spanning last 2 weeks (mood levels 2-5, energy levels 2-5)\n198\t- 5-8 SymptomEntries with varied types and severities\n199\t- 3-4 DoctorVisits with realistic summaries\n200\t- 4-6 Reminders (mix of done and pending, next checkup in 5 days)\n201\t- 42 WeekContent entries (one per pregnancy week, with size comparisons, body changes, baby development)\n202\t- 4 SelfCareCheckState items per day (prenatal vitamins, hydration, kegel exercises, gentle stretching)\n203\t- 10-15 Articles across all 4 topics\n204\t- 8-12 Exercises across all 3 categories (breathing, stretching, meditation)\n205\t- 1 UserPreferences with defaults (kg, all notifications on, reduced motion off)\n206\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a74ff47c-f0fd-427b-86f4-237d93787cf9","uuid":"a372ba60-61df-4